metadata.name: Bear Market Deal
metadata.description:
The bear had taken over the mine a long time ago and was not letting anyone in. He believed that having everything alone would bring him happiness but all he had was solitude. Pepe entered the mine in anger. He used his strongest weapon and hugged.sometimes you have to sacrifice for a happy ending.
